@xingchun-chen You cannot directly authorize a directory without files in it. As you said, there is only one file in the directory, and the directory and files are created by the directory creator.
 
目录中如果没有文件是无法对目录直接授权的，如您所说目录中只有一个文件，目录以及文件都是由目录创建者创建。
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7664170/96571998-e81add80-12fe-11eb-8200-b02920c83104.png)

@xingchun-chen My version is 1.3.2 Release. After user A creates the directory, can you grant the directory permission to user B through the administrator?What is your version?

